You have connected too fast. You must wait at least 4 seconds between connections.

我写的插件，连接到BC的通道，使用的是
ByteArrayDataOutput out = ByteStreams.newDataOutput();
out.writeUTF("ConnectOther");
out.writeUTF(playerName);
out.writeUTF(serverName);

但是我发现，多个人同时使用跳转，只会有一个人进去，其他人会出现
You have connected too fast. You must wait at least 4 seconds between connections.
您连接的速度太快。 您必须在连接之间等待至少4秒。

求助如何解决，拜谢大神
